---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Privacy Policy | freellm.site"
  description="Privacy policy for freellm.site — how we collect, use, and protect your data when you use our free LLM API directory."
>
  <article class="legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: June 28, 2026</p>
    <p class="legal-lead">
      freellm.site ("we", "us", "our") operates a free directory of LLM API providers.
      This policy explains what information we collect and how we use it.
    </p>

    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <p>When you visit freellm.site, we and our third-party partners may automatically collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Browser type, device type, and operating system</li>
      <li>Pages visited, time spent, and referring URL</li>
      <li>Approximate geographic location (country/region level)</li>
      <li>IP address (processed by third-party services)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not require account registration and do not collect names, email addresses, or payment information through this site unless you contact us directly.</p>

    <h2>How we use information</h2>
    <p>We use collected information to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Understand how visitors use the site and improve content</li>
      <li>Measure traffic and page performance</li>
      <li>Serve relevant advertisements</li>
      <li>Detect and prevent abuse or technical issues</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <p>We use the following third-party services that may collect data:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — website traffic and usage analytics. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — display advertising. Google and its partners may use cookies to serve ads based on your visits to this and other websites. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">How Google uses advertising cookies</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — website hosting and content delivery.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a> or <a href="https://optout.aboutads.info/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">aboutads.info</a>.</p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies and similar technologies for analytics and advertising. For details, see our <a href="/cookies/">Cookie Policy</a>. You can manage cookie preferences using the banner shown on your first visit.</p>

    <h2>Data retention</h2>
    <p>Analytics and advertising data is retained according to each third-party provider's policies. We do not maintain a separate database of visitor personal information.</p>

    <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
    <p>freellm.site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, or delete personal data. To exercise these rights or ask questions about this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@freellm.site">contact@freellm.site</a>.</p>

    <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this privacy policy? Email <a href="mailto:contact@freellm.site">contact@freellm.site</a> or visit our <a href="/contact/">Contact page</a>.</p>
  </article>
</Base>
